displayName: Photizona Royal Palace Underground Dungeon B1

parameters:
Sinner Pecado: The day of execution is near... Please hurry
and help me.

Sinner Pecado: 'I have no regrets anymore... except for the
fact that that bastard Shimos is still alive.'
Clea: I came from the Adventurer's Guild.

Sinner Pecado: You're quite a cute young lady. Come over
here and show me your face more often.
Clea: I've been told not to get too close.

Sinner Pecado: Haha, it's like being treated like an animal.
But the reason I asked you to come today is because I have a
favor to ask.

Sinner Pecado: I used to belong to the Tomosu Raiders in the
past. They were a bunch of hopeless scoundrels whose job was
literally plundering.
Clea: Does that story have something to do with the request?

Sinner Pecado: ...Though I may be scum, I had some pride and
never stole from defenseless humans.

Sinner Pecado: Except for that one time... what I want to
request is a penance to the Campos Church.

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, I am a priestess of Campos. I can
directly hear your sins here, you know?

Sinner Pecado: What a coincidence, I'm grateful to Deirei!
However, I used to be part of a plundering gang. I believe
that penance should be repaid in kind.

Sinner Pecado: I have a treasure map here, but instead of
me, could you make a donation to the Campos Church?
Clea: Understood, I will accept your request.

Sinner Pecado: Thank you... With this, I have no regrets.
Also, please tell that bastard Shimos to die 100 times!

Sinner Pecado: The Tomosu Raiders haven't given up on
seeking revenge against you.
Clea: The request has been completed.

Sinner Pecado: I hate you guys, adventurers from the rival
guild, but I have to admit that relying on you for this
request was the right choice... Your work is reliable, after
all...

Simos of the Unknown Night: Hahaha, what a coincidence! I
also hate filthy rats like you guys.
Thief Nora: Ah, s-someone scary is here!!

Simos of the Unknown Night: It seems like it's about time
for execution. So, was it worth keeping you alive and
capturing you?

Simos of the Unknown Night: Tell me the whereabouts of
Tomos' plundering gang. I don't want to bother killing each
one of you individually, it's a hassle.

Sinner Pecado: The answer is the same as back then. Even if
I die, I won't betray my comrades, especially not to you.

Simos of the Unknown Night: I see... I'll make sure my
comrades follow right behind you soon.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Clea, it seems like you got
promoted, huh?

Clea: Yes, with this, we have taken one step closer to the
dragon.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Dragons, huh... Everyone here
seems to have their heads in the clouds, it's annoying.

Simos of the Unknown Night: Don't forget that adventurers
are the ones who resolve conflicts, and violence is at the
core of that, you know?

Mage Relm: You really have a terrible personality...! What
kind of life did you live to become such a person!

Sinner Pecado: Our territory was around Fotizona, but Agonia
and Simos almost completely destroyed it.

Sinner Pecado: We, who were just a plundering gang, have
turned into assassins targeting the Adventurers Guild.

Sinner Pecado: You should be careful too. Everyone involved
with the Adventurers Guild is our enemy.
Fotizona Guard: Stay away, he's a dangerous prisoner.
Insect User Sarigari: What have I done...
Insect User Saligari: You guys... from that time...!
Clea: I have something I want to ask you today.

Insect User Saligari: Your thoughts are correct. There is a
back entrance that is not used in the Kasaro Bathhouse.

Insect User Saligari: I used it to sneak into the boiler
room every night.
Clea: Can you tell me the location?

Insect User Saligari: It's a passage for the workers that
was used during construction. There are very few who know
about this passage.
Clea: Thank you for telling me about such a place...

Insect User Saligari: I wonder if it's possible to make
amends, even after committing a crime?

Insect User Saligari: The warden is telling me that it's
about time for my release and wants to hire me.

Clea: I believe that if you truly want to start over and
continue fighting, it is possible.

Insect User Saligari: Thank you for stopping me at that
time. I would like to meet you at the Kasaro Bathhouse next
time.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Insect User Sarigari: What have I done...

Hayato's Irritation: Even a genius pickpocket can't beat
age...
